[I] A library for building native apps with the BeOS API

[T] Cosmoe is a C++ class library that allows developers to build native
[T] graphical apps for all major platforms with the powerful but easy-to-use
[T] BeOS API, using a single codebase. This library targets Wayland, X11,
[T] MacOS, and Windows graphical environments.

[U] https://gitlab.com/haydentech/cosmoe/

[A] Haiku, Inc
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/x11
[F] CROSS

